Just make sure you follow the instructions closely! You will have to disable virus protection if you use the keygen as it's a false positive.

For v.1800 I used:

ID: 5AQ338WW2N
SERIAL: HB6F-A9KU-TYYL-K8N4

If this one gets blocked, generate your own key as I did from: http://thepiratebay.org/torrent/6058280/Malwarebytes_Anti-Malware_1.50.1.1100___Keygens_%5BRH%5D

If you use the keygen from here, make sure you disable your antivirus as it will detect it as a false positive. ALSO, MAKE SURE YOU FOLLOW THE DIRECTIONS CLOSELY!! If you have the keygen opened while MWB is open, it will detect it and disable that key as well. (A feature added by MWB to make it impossible for pirates who don't follow directions to install the software).
